scitokens-cpp
------------------------------------------
SciTokens provide a token format for distributed authorization. The tokens are
self-describing, can be verified in a distributed fashion (no need to contact
the issuer to determine if the token is valid). This is convenient for a
federated environment where several otherwise-independent storage endpoints
want to delegate trust for an issuer for managing a storage allocation.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.4.6-1
  libSciTokens-devel-0.7.3-1bl1
  libSciTokens0-0.7.3-1bl1
  libcurl4-7.88.1-1
  libgcc1-11.3.0-1
  libsqlite3_0-3.34.0-1
  libssl1.1-1.1.1t-1
  libstdc++6-11.3.0-1
  libuuid1-2.33.1-2
  pkg-config-1.9.4-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.40-1
  cmake-3.23.2-1
  cygport-0.36.0-1
  gcc-core-11.3.0-1
  gcc-g++-11.3.0-1
  libcurl-devel-7.88.1-1
  libsqlite3-devel-3.34.0-1
  libssl-devel-1.1.1t-1
  libuuid-devel-2.33.1-2
  ninja-1.11.1-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/scitokens/scitokens-cpp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/scitokens/scitokens-cpp.git

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack scitokens-cpp-0.7.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./scitokens-cpp-0.7.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/scitokens-cpp-0.7.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/scitokens-cpp-0.7.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libSciTokens0-0.7.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libSciTokens-devel-0.7.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(scitokens-cpp)
  /usr/bin/scitokens-create.exe
  /usr/bin/scitokens-list-access.exe
  /usr/bin/scitokens-test-access.exe
  /usr/bin/scitokens-test.exe
  /usr/bin/scitokens-verify.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/scitokens-cpp.README
  /usr/share/doc/scitokens-cpp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/scitokens-cpp/README.md

(libSciTokens0)
  /usr/bin/cygSciTokens-0.dll

(libSciTokens-devel)
  /usr/include/scitokens/scitokens.h
  /usr/lib/libSciTokens.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/scitokens-cpp.pc

